OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775408752
OL,3,CWoman who's survived three strokes and
OL,4,Chad 13 heart ops says she feels
OL,5,C'blessed'
OL,7,FMichelle White spoke to ITV Granada
OL,8,FReports correspondent Andy Bonner.
OL,10,FA woman from Manchester who's survived
OL,11,Fthree strokes and had 13 heart
OL,12,Fprocedures says she feels "blessed" at
OL,13,Fbeing able to tell her story.
OL,15,FMichelle White collapsed at work and
OL,16,Fwas later found to have a faulty heart
OL,17,Fvalve, aged just 26.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
