FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775408752
OL,3,CWoman who's survived three strokes and
OL,4,Chad 13 heart ops says she feels
OL,5,C'blessed'
OL,7,FHer heart then became enlarged due to
OL,8,Fthe extra strain it was under, and she
OL,9,Fhad two open-heart surgeries to repair
OL,10,Fthe faulty valve. As a result, she
OL,11,Fdeveloped several abnormal heart
OL,12,Frhythms and had a pacemaker fitted.
OL,14,FThen in 2009, Michelle had a major
OL,15,Fstroke. After returning from her mum's
OL,16,Ffriends retirement party, she woke up
OL,17,Fin the early hours of the morning
OL,18,Ffeeling unwell.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
