OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775408752
OL,3,CWoman who's survived three strokes and
OL,4,Chad 13 heart ops says she feels
OL,5,C'blessed'
OL,7,F"I tried to get out of bed but just
OL,8,Ffell to the ground," said Michelle,
OL,9,Fnow aged 49.
OL,11,F"My eldest son ran in and he
OL,12,Fimmediately called the paramedics and
OL,13,Fmy mum and sister. His quick actions
OL,14,Fhelped saved my life."
OL,16,FThe stroke left her unable to walk or
OL,17,Ftalk and the mother-of-three had to
OL,18,Fundergo intensive physiotherapy and
OL,19,Fspeech therapy. Miraculously, she made
OL,20,Fa good recovery and was discharged
OL,21,Fafter six months.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@TO]sD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
