OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775408752
OL,3,CWoman who's survived three strokes and
OL,4,Chad 13 heart ops says she feels
OL,5,C'blessed'
OL,7,FHowever, Michelle has faced further
OL,8,Fissues with her heart and was also re-
OL,9,Fadmitted to hospital following another
OL,10,Fstroke in 2011 and one in 2022.
OL,12,FThen in 2023, she became very unwell
OL,13,Fagain and was told she was going to
OL,14,Fneed lifesaving surgery to replace one
OL,15,Fheart valve and repair another ` which
OL,16,Ftook nine hours.
OL,18,FMichelle added, "My heart has a
OL,19,Fpersonality of its own ` it does just
OL,20,Fenough to push the boundaries.
OL,26,@zD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
