OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775408752
OL,3,CWoman who's survived three strokes and
OL,4,Chad 13 heart ops says she feels
OL,5,C'blessed'
OL,7,F"My youngest son's first memories of
OL,8,Fme are shaped by my heart condition,
OL,9,Fseeing me on a life support machine,
OL,10,Fbut they've also shaped my sense of
OL,11,Fpurpose."
OL,13,FNow Michelle, from Didsbury, is one of
OL,14,F65 people across the UK to receive an
OL,15,Ficonic red bench in her "living
OL,16,Fmemory" as part of a new campaign for
OL,17,Fthe British Heart Foundation.
OL,19,FIt was unveiled at the New Testament
OL,20,FChurch of God, Old Trafford, on Easter
OL,21,FSunday (March 5).
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775408752
OL,3,CWoman who's survived three strokes and
OL,4,Chad 13 heart ops says she feels
OL,5,C'blessed'
OL,7,FMichelle said: "It was deeply
OL,8,Fimportant to me to have the bench
OL,9,Fplaced at my church - the same church
OL,10,Fmy Grandma and Grandad attended when
OL,11,Fit first opened, and where my children
OL,12,Fwere christened.
OL,14,F"My faith is an integral part of my
OL,15,Fjourney as a heart patient and a
OL,16,Fsource of strength during my most
OL,17,Fchallenging times."
OL,26,@oD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
