OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775408752
OL,3,CWoman who's survived three strokes and
OL,4,Chad 13 heart ops says she feels
OL,5,C'blessed'
OL,7,FShe told friends and family outside
OL,8,Fthe church, "Some people say it's so
OL,9,Funlucky but for me, I don't feel like
OL,10,FI'm unlucky.
OL,12,F"I feel like I'm blessed because in
OL,13,Fthe journey that I've been on, I've
OL,14,Fbeen able to share my story with
OL,15,Fmillions of people.
OL,17,F"Even if I inspire one person, it's
OL,18,Fokay."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
