OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775408752
OL,3,CWoman who's survived three strokes and
OL,4,Chad 13 heart ops says she feels
OL,5,C'blessed'
OL,7,FHer experience also inspired her to
OL,8,Fset up her own styling business,
OL,9,FHeartfelt Styling, which aims to make
OL,10,Fpeople feel good in their clothes
OL,11,Ffollowing illness.
OL,13,F"I won't let fear define me," said
OL,14,FMichelle.
OL,16,F"I'm taking things step by step,
OL,17,Fstaying positive, and I feel I'm at a
OL,18,Fnew chapter where I can focus on what
OL,19,Ftruly matters most."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@]O]xD@AOU{D@TO]
